<p>Ipamorelin changed the game. It's the first truly selective ghrelin receptor agonist, meaning it stimulates growth hormone release without touching other hormonal pathways. For people interested in <a href="/articles/best-peptides-for-anti-aging">anti-aging</a> and recovery, that selectivity makes all the difference.</p>

